verbose_text: To determine whether SIX1/Cdc42/VEGFA expression is negatively correlated with miR-4306 expression in breast tumors, qPCR was used to measure the mRNA expression levels in the same samples in which we had previously measured miR-4306 expression levels in Figure XREF_FIG (242 tumors and their pair matched adjacent normal tissues from 98 patients with luminal-type breast cancer, 25 patients with HER2-type breast cancer and 119 patients with TNBC).
